@#30300
Outside gates~
Solid steel gates stand wide open as you approach the city. The gates are a 
foot wide! Magic must help open and close them, they are far too heavy to be 
moved by the hand of man. The tall city walls stretch 50 feet above the ground 
and through the open gates you can see the walls themselve are 30 or 40 feet 
of solid stone. Only a very large army or one with powerful magic wielding 
allies could hope to take the city without been slaughtered.
~
