Southern highway~
Travelling along the highway you pass a merchants caravan heading towards
the city. A handful of guards ride alongside the wagons, looking like tree
trunks on horses, their arms as thick as most mens thighs. The only thing
harder then their muscles is probably the 'wood' between their ears.
