#30429
Wall~
Set into the back of the wall stone stairs lead down into the wall itself. 
Back along the wall soldiers march up and down it's length, keeping their 
eyes cast outward. Though they stand here to protect the city, they never 
look into it, leaving the city watch to patrol within its walls.
