#30441
Stairs up~
A small set of stone stairs set within the wall will take you up to the 
top of the city wall. Next to the stairs are two doors, banded with iron 
and very thick. Glancing through the open doors you can see what appears 
to be quarters through one door, a small mess hall through the other. 
