and the inner city, nestled at the foot of a 'curve' in the mountain, 
protected along its southern edge by another wall. All are welcome in the 
main part of the city, but the inner city contains the wheels of government 
and homes of the cities nobles and the likes of you aren't allowed entry 
without a gate pass.
~
