Outside sea caves~
Sheer cliffs rise out of the water, the sea pounding up against them, ready 
to crush anyone foolish enough to venture too close. A small cave enterance 
is visible between the rocks, but it would take a brave sailor to try and 
move a boat in that close without magic as an aid.
